@terrymanu it could use the following codes to set the properties
```
PropertyUtils.setProperties(this.xaDataSource, this.xaProperties);
```

pay_cmdy: 
  actualDataNodes: pay_${0..15}.pay_cmdy_000${0..9}
  databaseStrategy: 
    inline:
      shardingColumn: payment_no
      algorithmExpression: pay_${payment_no % 16}
  tableStrategy: 
    inline:
      shardingColumn: payment_no
      algorithmExpression: pay_cmdy_000${payment_no % 10}
